                  <span class="c00">&gt; I don&#x27;t understand how you can attach strings (i.e. conditions ) on gifts, telling the receipt how they can or cannot use the gift.<p>Simple, you just attach covenants to the gift.  You can do the same with real property (such as during the sale of land), which restricts the ways in which a property can be used: <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Covenant_(law)" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Covenant_(law)</a><span>
